pPodVersionInfo

private PPodVersionInfo pPodVersionInfo
The pPod-version of this object. Similar in concept to Hibernate's version, but tweaked for our purposes.

Will be saved in PPodVersionInfoInterceptor and it's because its manipulated in there that we need to leave it eagerly fetched.

resetPPodVersionInfo

protected PPodEntity resetPPodVersionInfo()
Mark this object's PPodVersionInfo for update to the next version number on save or update. This is done by setting it to null.

Implementors should also, if desired, call resetPPodVersionInfo() on any owning objects.

Returns:
this PPodEntity
